    "description": "Settle Gliese is a collaborative storytelling game set in a massive dangerous world. It’s a mixture of a roguelike and a text-based roleplaying game.<br><br><strong>Familiar roguelike features you know and love</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Journey through wild continents and discover the settlements and communities of other players<br></li><li>Unique biomes<br></li><li>Turn-based dice rolling combat </li></ul><br><strong>Take on a role</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>‘Play-act’ the character as they live out their life<br></li><li>Focus on building, creativity, and society<br></li><li>Intimate interactions in a safe space with roleplaying rules<br></li><li>Talk, write notices for others, and craft personal items and artworks to shape the society they are a part of. </li></ul><br><strong>In a Massively Multiplayer World</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collaborate to advance and survive<br></li><li>Shape the world <br></li><li>Uncover its secrets</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387700/extras/0f7ec4c84b512449a8d0496a3d392323.poster.avif?t=1771443105\" width=786 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387700/extras/0f7ec4c84b512449a8d0496a3d392323.webm?t=1771443105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387700/extras/0f7ec4c84b512449a8d0496a3d392323.mp4?t=1771443105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
